Package com.binance.connector.futures.client.impl.cm_futures

Class CMMarket

java.lang.Object
com.binance.connector.futures.client.impl.futures.Market
com.binance.connector.futures.client.impl.cm_futures.CMMarket
public class CMMarket extends Market

Coin-Margined Market Endpoints

All endpoints under the Market Data Endpoint section of the API documentation will be implemented in this class.
Response will be returned in String format.
